<title>FRANCE: SocGen upgrades rating on Promodes.</title>
<headline>SocGen upgrades rating on Promodes.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1996-09-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Investment firm Societe Generale raised its recommendation on retailer Promodes's stock to outperform from neutral following the sale of its money-losing German unit Promohypermarkt to the Spar Handels chain, traders said.</p>
<p>Promodes's stock was down 0.16 percent at 1,216 at 1130 GMT, faring better than the Paris bourse's CAC-40 index which was 1.23 percent lower.</p>
<p>-- Paris Newsroom, +33 1 4221 5452</p>
